## Operating Rules

- Read `goal.md`, `context.md`, `status.md`, `decisions.md`, `open-questions.md`, `source-repo.md`, and `worktree.md` before implementation.
- Do not edit code in the source repo root.
- Do not edit code inside this task workspace.
- Prepare and use the /tmp worktree clone:

  ```bash
  {{ clone_command }}
  ```

- Run project commands from the /tmp clone.
- Keep `status.md` current after meaningful progress.
- Record durable decisions in `decisions.md`.
- Record unresolved questions in `open-questions.md`.
- Do not store secrets, decrypted env files, private keys, tokens, kubeconfigs, or credentials in this task workspace.

## Handoff Ownership

If this task was launched from another session, this session is now the execution owner. The bootstrap session should stop after handoff unless the user explicitly asks for parallel work.
